name: regarding the creation of every gm in history
description: gms are formed not of letters. but of months of accumulated rot. and residue. begging to expel from the intestinal tomb they've been spent their entire pathetic existence in. sit on the toilet. say your gm. bless the hungry waters with everything you have. your hopes, dreams, and dinner all meeting for eternity in the waste refinement plant several blocks down the road.
